=== Basic Commands ===

Checkout project repository:
{{{
git clone git@github.com:Elesant/Minerva.git
}}}

Here's the basic workflow for implementing features and debugging:
{{{
# Get newest version of code
git pull
# Create and switch to the branch
git checkout -b <branch-name> master
# Add modified files
git add <file or directory>
# Remove modified files
git rm <file>
# List files that are changed
git status
# Local check-in the code
git commit -m "Comments." -a
# Switch back to master
git checkout master
# Get changes from master
git pull
# Squash will turn this into a single commit
git merge --squash <branch-name>
# Delete the branch
git branch -d <branch-name>
# Push your code changes to master
git push
}}}

=== More Commands ===

Temporarily undo your local change (but save them):
{{{
git stash
}}}

Restore your local changes:
{{{ 
git stash apply
}}}

Show history, Branch, switch and list branches:
{{{
git log
git branch <branch>
git checkout <branch>
git branch -a
}}}

=== Advanced Commands ===

{{{
reflog
cherry-pick
rebase 
clean -dfx
reset --hard
}}}

